      95-0075.)  No one objected to submitting this for a formal vote.
 
8.3   Extensions WG
 
      Stroustrup summarized the WG's most recent deliberations.  The WG con-
      sidered:
      --  adding typedef templates to C++.  The WG decided they would not be
          that useful.
 
 
